, 172.981, 174.5451, 174.9347, 176.8666, 178.1823, 178.6754, 180.0821, 180.054, 181.5492, 180.5979, 177.5474, 179.5535, 179.9283, 180.1849, 178.7236, 176.4978, 176.0743, 176.4428, 178.8467, 178.2341, 178.749, 179.6112, 180.5441, 182.601, 182.0852, 183.7553, 183.4583, 183.8224, 187.0788, 190.6358, 187.0308, 186.4234, 188.0202, 187.9419, 189.1305, 188.3528, 187.022, 185.6047, 186.1656, 186.3545, 187.0197, 187.8004, 188.0262, 187.3485, 189.4033, 191.2432, 187.1035, 183.9862, 183.9391, 183.5937, 182.1551, 182.4279, 182.5722, 182.8783, 184.4828, 184.6001, 184.6435, 185.3483, 186.3964, 186.6464, 187.9437, 187.8417, 187.5248, 187.9059, 187.2339, 189.6715, 194.1038, 191.5132, 196.2678, 198.923, 197.7245, 198.3776, 199.7592, 198.5053, 197.0252, 198.8514, 198.7156, 197.898, 196.7133, 199.0335, 198.259, 197.9589, 198.1008, 196.0241], "summary_html": "<h1>港股因子有效性和组合设计 -- 跨资产复现</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本报告测试了104个港股中低频因子（79个财务因子+25个量价因子），最终筛选出7个表现最优因子构建多因子组合。跨资产复现时，将这7个股票因子的核心逻辑迁移到商品期货市场：动量类因子（价格距高点比率、残差动量）直接计算，低波动溢价因子（特质波动率）使用回归残差标准差，彩票效应因子（最大日收益）使用滚动极值，价值因子用展期收益率（ry）替代市盈率（ni_me），盈利质量因子用利润数据（profit）替代QMJ_Prof。</p>\n<p>该策略的alpha来源是多因子组合的分散化效应：各因子捕捉不同维度的定价偏差（动量延续、低波溢价、价值回归、盈利质量），组合后降低了单因子的波动性。IC gate进一步过滤了信号在品种维度无效的时段，提升了信号噪比。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.93</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>6.6%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>7.1%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-17.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.05</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.22</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.61</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.12 / 1.31</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.83</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.52</span></td><td>1.43</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.66</span></td><td>1.81</td><td>0.86</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.22</span></td><td>0.4</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.28</span></td><td>1.93</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.18</span></td><td>0.44</td><td>1.07</td><td>1.47</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.35</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ry</code></td><td>展期收益</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>profit</code></td><td>利润</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>38.2%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>15.8</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>Factor 1: Price-to-High (prc_highprc_252d)</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">F_1 = \\frac{P_t}{\\max(P_{t-252}, \\ldots, P_t)}</div>\n<p><strong>Factor 2: Residual Momentum (resid_mom_252d)</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">r^{resid}_t = r_t - \\beta_t \\cdot r^{mkt}_t, \\quad \\beta_t = \\frac{Cov_{60d}(r, r^{mkt})}{Var_{60d}(r^{mkt})}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">F_2 = \\sum_{i=t-252}^{t-21} r^{resid}_i</div>\n<p><strong>Factor 3-4: Idiosyncratic Volatility (ivol_252d, ivol_21d)</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">F_{3} = \\sigma_{252d}(r^{resid}), \\quad F_{4} = \\sigma_{21d}(r^{resid})</div>\n<p><strong>Factor 5: Max Return (rmax5_21d)</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">F_5 = \\max(r_{t-20}, \\ldots, r_t)</div>\n<p><strong>Factor 6: Carry</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">F_6 = ry_t \\quad \\text{(roll yield)}</div>\n<p><strong>Factor 7: Profit Quality</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">F_7 = profit_t</div>\n<p><strong>Composite Signal:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">S_t = \\frac{1}{N_{valid}} \\sum_{i=1}^{7} d_i \\cdot rank_{cs}(F_i)</div>\n<p>where <span class=\"math-tex\">d_i \\in \\{+1, -1\\}</span> is the factor direction, <span class=\"math-tex\">rank_{cs}</span> maps to <span class=\"math-tex\">[-1, 1]</span>.</p>\n<p><strong>IC Gate</strong>: Rolling 252d correlation <span class=\"math-tex\">\\rho(S_{t-1}, r_t)</span> per symbol. Only trade symbols where <span class=\"math-tex\">\\rho &gt; 0</span>.</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.91)</strong>: 初始实现全部7个因子的跨资产翻译。保持研报原始方向：动量/价值/盈利为正向，波动率/彩票为负向。21日再平衡，等权组合。combo_7f_eq_raw达0.91，单因子中carry最强(0.61)，ivol因子为负(-0.31/-0.42)说明低波溢价在商品期货未必成立。</p>\n<p><strong>R2 (Sharpe 1.00)</strong>: 诊断R1的问题：(1) ivol负Sharpe拖累组合，测试翻转方向；(2) 21日hold可能太长。行动：增加方向翻转变体、hold_days网格(10/21/42)。结果：h10(10日hold)最优，Sharpe从0.91提升到1.00。翻转方向未改善。关键发现：更短的再平衡频率显著提升了组合表现。</p>\n<p><strong>R3 (Sharpe 1.05)</strong>: 诊断R2的问题：ts_ic仅0.003，信号在部分品种有效。行动：(1) sym_rolling_ic_gate过滤弱品种；(2) hold_days精细网格(5/8/10/15/21)；(3) vol_target网格(0.10/0.15/0.20)。结果：IC gate是关键转折点，通过过滤滚动IC&lt;=0的品种-时段组合，Sharpe从1.00提升到1.05，且第二半段(1.49)显著优于第一半段(0.63)，说明信号在近年加速有效。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频 (<code>comm_data/daily/kline_daynight_all.parquet</code>)</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（~58个活跃品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 10个交易日再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 截面IC较低(0.008)，策略更多靠信号在时间维度的持续性和分散化\n<p>- 与因子库中 <code>20221230_xinda_ret_std_imp</code> 相关性0.58，存在一定冗余 - ivol因子（低波溢价）在商品期货表现为负，可能因为商品的高波动往往伴随趋势 - profit和ry字段覆盖率有限（~27%/~37%），部分品种无这两个因子的贡献</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.94s</li>\n</ul>"}